# Source of truth for dev-time dependencies (contributor machines + CI).
# Edit this file, NOT requirements-dev.txt.
#
# `-r requirements.in` pulls in every runtime dep so one install covers both.
#
# Regenerate the hashed requirements-dev.txt after editing:
#     ./venv/bin/pip-compile --allow-unsafe --generate-hashes --resolver=backtracking requirements-dev.in
#
# (See requirements.in for the explanation of --allow-unsafe; same
# rationale applies here.)

-r requirements.in

